<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - WebAppApiPhim</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
</head>
<body class="bg-dark text-light">
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark border-bottom box-shadow mb-3">
            <div class="container">
                <a class="navbar-brand d-flex align-items-center" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">
                    <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" height="40" class="me-2">
                    <div>
                        <span class="fw-bold">Phim</span>
                        <small class="d-block" style="font-size: 0.7rem; margin-top: -5px;">Phim hay có rồ</small>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target=".navbar-collapse" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                        aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="navbar-collapse collapse d-sm-inline-flex justify-content-between">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-grow-1 mx-lg-4">
                        <form class="w-100" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Search" method="get">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-text bg-dark border-secondary text-light">
                                    <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                                </span>
                                <input type="text" name="keyword" class="form-control bg-dark border-secondary text-light" placeholder="Tìm kiếm phim, diễn viên">
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="navbar-nav">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-light" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Category" asp-route-id="chu-de">Chủ Đề</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-light" href="#" id="theloaiDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                                Thể loại
                            </a>
                            <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-dark" aria-labelledby="theloaiDropdown">
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Category" asp-route-id="hanh-dong">Hành động</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Category" asp-route-id="tinh-cam">Tình cảm</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Category" asp-route-id="hai-huoc">Hài hước</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Category" asp-route-id="co-trang">Cổ trang</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Category" asp-route-id="tam-ly">Tâm lý</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Category" asp-route-id="hinh-su">Hình sự</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Category" asp-route-id="kinh-di">Kinh dị</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Category" asp-route-id="vien-tuong">Viễn tưởng</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-light" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Type" asp-route-id="phim-le">Phim Lẻ</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-light" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Type" asp-route-id="phim-bo">Phim Bộ</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-light" href="#" id="quocgiaDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                                Quốc gia
                            </a>
                            <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-dark" aria-labelledby="quocgiaDropdown">
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Country" asp-route-id="viet-nam">Việt Nam</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Country" asp-route-id="trung-quoc">Trung Quốc</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Country" asp-route-id="han-quoc">Hàn Quốc</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Country" asp-route-id="nhat-ban">Nhật Bản</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Country" asp-route-id="thai-lan">Thái Lan</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Country" asp-route-id="au-my">Âu Mỹ</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-light" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Actors">Diễn Viên</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-light" asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Schedule">Lịch chiếu</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center ms-lg-3">
                        @if (User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
                        {
                            <div class="dropdown me-3">
                                <a class="btn btn-dark border-secondary dropdown-toggle d-flex align-items-center" href="#" role="button" id="userDropdown" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                                    <img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="User" class="rounded-circle me-2" width="24" height="24">
                                    <span>@User.Identity.Name</span>
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-dark" aria-labelledby="userDropdown">
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="User" asp-action="Profile">Tài khoản</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="User" asp-action="Favorites">Phim yêu thích</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="User" asp-action="WatchHistory">Lịch sử xem</a></li>
                                    <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                                    <li>
                                        <form asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Logout" method="post">
                                            <button type="submit" class="dropdown-item">Đăng xuất</button>
                                        </form>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <a class="btn btn-outline-light me-2" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Login">
                                <i class="fas fa-user me-1"></i> Đăng nhập
                            </a>
                            <a class="btn btn-light" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">
                                <i class="fas fa-user-plus me-1"></i> Thành viên
                            </a>
                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="border-top footer text-light bg-dark mt-5 py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <a class="navbar-brand d-flex align-items-center mb-3" href="#">
                        <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" height="40" class="me-2">
                        <div>
                            <span class="fw-bold">RoPhim</span>
                            <small class="d-block" style="font-size: 0.7rem; margin-top: -5px;">Phim hay có rồ</small>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                        <a href="#" class="me-2 btn btn-dark rounded-circle">
                            <i class="fab fa-telegram"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="me-2 btn btn-dark rounded-circle">
                            <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="me-2 btn btn-dark rounded-circle">
                            <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="me-2 btn btn-dark rounded-circle">
                            <i class="fab fa-tiktok"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="me-2 btn btn-dark rounded-circle">
                            <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-dark rounded-circle">
                            <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-danger text-white d-inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded">
                        <i class="fas fa-flag me-1"></i> Hoàng Sa & Trường Sa là của Việt Nam!
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3">
                            <h6>Thông tin</h6>
                            <ul class="nav flex-column">
                                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Hỏi-Đáp</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Chính sách bảo mật</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Điều khoản sử dụng</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Giới thiệu</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Liên hệ</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3">
                            <h6>Thể loại phim</h6>
                            <ul class="nav flex-column">
                                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Dongphim</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Ghienphim</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Motphim</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Subhanah</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                            <p class="text-secondary small">
                                Trang xem phim online chất lượng cao miễn phí Vietsub, thuyết minh, lồng tiếng full HD.<br>
                                Kho phim mới không lỗ, phim chiếu rạp, phim bộ, phim lẻ từ nhiều quốc gia như Việt Nam, Hàn Quốc, Trung Quốc,
                                Thái Lan, Nhật Bản, Âu Mỹ... đa dạng thể loại. Khám phá nền tảng phim trực tuyến hay nhất 2024 chất lượng 4K!
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-secondary small">© 2024 WebAppApiPhim</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    @await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>